HEADWORD: Flammivomous
<hw>Flam*miv"o*mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>flammivomus</ets>; <ets>flamma</ets> flame + <ets>vomere</ets> to
